<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="in-trouble">in trouble</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>处于困境中：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We should trust our friends, respect them and always be ready to help them when they are in trouble. 
我们应信任并尊重我们的朋友，在他们有困难的时候帮助他们。</p></div></div>